WEBVTT

00:00.501 --> 00:01.893
Previously on "The Originals"...

00:01.894 --> 00:03.062
Mary: We gather together

00:03.063 --> 00:06.803
with the unification
of the two crescent bloodlines.

00:06.804 --> 00:08.964
Hayley will share
here unique gifts

00:09.456 --> 00:10.418
with her pack.

00:10.419 --> 00:12.027
Let Jackson have Hayley.

00:12.028 --> 00:14.775
His reign
will be short-lived.

00:14.776 --> 00:18.052
Klaus: Jackson, I invite you
to live here.

00:18.053 --> 00:19.274
Welcome to the family.

00:19.275 --> 00:21.647
Well, the wolves are unified,
hope is safe,

00:21.648 --> 00:23.394
so in the interest of
maintaining the peace,

00:23.395 --> 00:26.308
I have decided to join
Marcel in algiers.

00:26.309 --> 00:27.443
- Rebekah.
- Freya.

00:27.444 --> 00:29.114
Tell our brothers
I'll be coming to see them.

00:29.115 --> 00:31.848
Gas has pervaded every
single room in this home.

00:31.849 --> 00:33.162
Good-bye, brother.

00:34.924 --> 00:39.037
Helbred bransar, belaste
herte, begin panet.

00:39.038 --> 00:40.506
I will not leave this body

00:40.507 --> 00:42.791
until I find a way
to bring you back.

00:42.792 --> 00:45.548
Hayley: Have you told
Marcel that you're you?

00:45.549 --> 00:47.659
I thought I'd hold off
on that for the moment.

00:48.593 --> 00:51.631
[Music playing]

00:58.436 --> 01:01.176
Enough already
with the family squabbling.

01:01.177 --> 01:02.445
Come on, Nik.
Even you can see

01:02.446 --> 01:04.813
how the situation
has become awkward.

01:04.813 --> 01:06.418
There's nothing
awkward about it.

01:06.419 --> 01:09.067
Hayley and hope belong in the
compound, where they're safe.

01:09.068 --> 01:11.196
As much as I would like
Elijah's help to kill Finn,

01:11.282 --> 01:13.093
if his delicate
sensibilities are offended

01:13.094 --> 01:14.864
by the presence
of Hayley's new husband,

01:14.865 --> 01:17.372
then he's welcome to continue
sulking across the river.

01:17.373 --> 01:19.213
As I have explained to you repeatedly,
brother,

01:19.214 --> 01:22.384
my presence here in algiers
is purely to assemble allies,

01:22.385 --> 01:24.053
and given all the
enemies we have afoot

01:24.054 --> 01:25.524
in the form of wayward siblings

01:25.525 --> 01:27.360
and ancient,
maniacal aunt dahlias,

01:27.361 --> 01:29.468
I would think that you
would applaud my efforts.

01:29.469 --> 01:31.105
Well, if it's my
applause you seek,

01:31.106 --> 01:32.776
you shouldn't have dashed
off in a bloody huff.

01:32.777 --> 01:34.645
Rebekah: All right.
Can you two at least try

01:34.646 --> 01:36.649
and stay focused on what's
best for hope's safety?

01:36.650 --> 01:38.118
I would like nothing more.

01:38.119 --> 01:39.320
I am doing exactly that.

01:39.321 --> 01:41.589
See? You're on the same team.

01:41.590 --> 01:44.793
Conflict resolved,
crisis averted.

01:46.000 --> 01:52.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:58.871 --> 02:00.200
Excuse you, too.

02:21.918 --> 02:23.386
Are you two looking
for something

02:23.387 --> 02:25.228
besides a smack in the jaw?

02:25.314 --> 02:27.103
You will die for
what you've done.

02:27.104 --> 02:28.103
Unh!

02:30.798 --> 02:32.774
Stupid bloody magic!

02:33.271 --> 02:34.818
Unh!

02:41.247 --> 02:42.535
There's more of them on the way.

02:42.536 --> 02:45.076
We should probably go.

02:45.077 --> 02:47.787
Rebekah.

02:47.788 --> 02:49.621
How did you know?

02:49.622 --> 02:50.788
Can we talk about that later?

02:50.789 --> 02:52.326
We don't have all day.

02:52.327 --> 02:56.692
Sync & corrections by <font color="#00ff00">Rafael UPD</font>
